 {"id":"beads_rust-bxo","title":"Changelog generation (closed issues grouped by type)","description":"# Changelog Generation (closed issues grouped by type)

## Purpose
Generate release notes from closed issues (port plan enhancement).

## CLI
```
br changelog --since <date|tag|commit> [--format markdown|json]
```

## Behavior
- Select issues where `closed_at > since`.
- Group by `issue_type`, sort by priority within group.
- Output Markdown or JSON.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Grouping and sorting match plan doc.
- Handles `--since-tag` and `--since-commit` (resolve via git when available).

## Tests
- Fixture DB with closed issues across types.
- Markdown output formatting.","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"feature","owner":"jeff141421@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-01-16T02:18:31.764223209-05:00","created_by":"Dicklesworthstone","updated_at":"2026-01-16T02:45:03.653744696-05:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"beads_rust-bxo","depends_on_id":"beads_rust-gs0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-16T02:47:09.049319106-05:00","created_by":"Dicklesworthstone"},{"issue_id":"beads_rust-bxo","depends_on_id":"beads_rust-554","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-16T02:53:02.152635349-05:00","created_by":"Dicklesworthstone"}]}
